fr.zelus.jarvis.plugins.mail.module.action

Class SendMail

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.zelus.jarvis.core.JarvisAction<MailModule>
      • fr.zelus.jarvis.plugins.mail.module.action.SendMail
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Callable<Object>

    public class SendMail
extends JarvisAction<MailModule>
    A JarvisAction that sends an email to the provided address with the given body and title.

    This class relies on the MailModule's Gmail service to connect to the corresponding Gmail account and send emails.

    See Also:
    MailModule
